perfcenter.baseclass

Class Machine

  • java.lang.Object
    • perfcenter.baseclass.Machine
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PhysicalMachine, VirtualMachine

    public class Machine
extends java.lang.Object
    This represents the machine definition in the input file. A machine can have software servers deployed onto them. Machine has set of devices and an machine is deployed on to a single LAN. Machine also has machine resources and devices deployed on them.
    Author:
    akhila, rakesh, bhavin
